cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "AGENTS.md: Operating Rules for Multi-Agent LLM Coding Teams"
message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Tang
    given-names: Junjie
repository-code: "https://github.com/JunjieTang-D1/agents-md"
url: "https://github.com/JunjieTang-D1/agents-md"
abstract: >-
  Five rules for multi-agent LLM coding teams, derived from 40 controlled
  experiments across 13 configurations, 5 team topologies, 2 domains, and
  2 model generations. Covers team size, directory structure, feedback
  loops, deployment ownership, and reproducibility reporting.
keywords:
  - multi-agent-systems
  - llm
  - software-engineering
  - operating-rules
  - agent-coordination
